    The Foundations Class is for kids who are just starting with coding. They teach you the basics so that way you know what you
    are doing. The teachers will talk to you about different things and teach you a lot of new tags. This class helps a lot when
    you are new and don't know what you are doing at all! BDPA's mission and vision is to be the premeir leader in STEM that engages,
    empowers, and drives thought leadership for our diverse commyunity. BDPA wants to make sure that we have the right skills in coding
    so we can be very successful in the future.
