<h2> Weekly Curriculum </h2>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Week</th>
    <th>Subject</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 1</td>
    <td>HTML Basics</td>
    <td>In this class you will learn the basic html code and different tags as well.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 2</td>
    <td>Website Layout</td>
    <td>For this class you will design what you want your websithe to look like on paper. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 3</td>
    <td>Getting your Computer  </td>
    <td>You will get your computer and set it up with the password and download some coding apps.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 4</td>
    <td>Adding Color </td>
    <td>This class will teach you how to adid color to the background and to your letters.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 5</td>
    <td>Images</td>
    <td>In this class you will learn how to add photos.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 6</td>
    <td>About Me </td>
    <td>You will start your about me page and what you want that to look like.</td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>Week 7</td>
    <td>Adding Links</td>
    <td>For this class you will learn how to add links to your website. </td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>Week 8</td>
    <td>Videos</td>
    <td>You will learn how to add videos to your website. </td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>Week 9</td>
    <td>Learning CSS</td>
    <td>In this class you will learn the basics of CSS and the new form of tags.</td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>Week 10</td>
    <td>CSS Webpage</td>
    <td>You will start on your webpage in the CSS format. </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>

